            From Inner Loop redevelopment to suburban builds—we cover Rochester contractors, roofers, electricians, and HVAC specialists.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• General contractors</li>
            <li>• Roofing contractors</li>
            <li>• Snow removal operations</li>
            <li>• Home improvement contractors</li>
            <li>• HVAC technicians</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Retail & Hospitality -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200">
